premise_source_doc_sentence: Naturi Cora Maria Naughton  (  born May 20 , 1984  )  is an American actress and singer-songwriter .

Lottery Ticket is a 2010 American comedy film directed by Erik White and starring Bow Wow , Brandon T. Jackson , Naturi Naughton , Keith David , Charlie Murphy , Gbenga Akinnagbe , Loretta Devine and Ice Cube in lead roles .
